#compdef proguardgui
# Documentation: https://www.guardsquare.com/en/products/proguard/manual/gui
# Reference accessed: 2026-05-20
# Verified: Guardsquare ProGuard GUI docs. Invoked as
# `java -jar proguardgui.jar [config.pro]`. Source code shows extra
